{"tid":1056762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖］勝利KKT對話房中的藝人有鄭俊英… 歌手崔某也一起","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T13:19:16.000Z","uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b626989cf9299ceab0dd83eb2c6fd9aba13dc4fa","tid":1056762,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"11日下午播放的SBS《8news》中報道稱,歌手鄭俊英在包含組合Bigbang勝利在內的Kakao Talk聊天室散布了非法拍攝視頻。<br />\n<br />\n拿到kakao talk對話內容的SBS方面表示:&quot;確認了對話內容沒有造假,為了防止損失,經過深思熟慮後決定公開藝人的實名。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n據SBS報道,2015年末鄭俊英向朋友金某炫耀自己和一個女性發生了性關係, 金某問&quot;沒有視頻嗎?&quot; 對此,鄭俊英傳送了偷拍的性關係視頻。 還給同僚藝人發送了郵件。 同一時期,還偷拍了酒吧女服務員的身體部位。<br />\n<br />\nSBS方面掌握的Kakao Talk對話內容為10個月的資料,在此過程中發現的非法拍攝受害者就有10人。 <br />\n另外,在相關聊天室中,歌手崔某等人散布的非法攝影也佔多數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6fiTNO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6fiTNO.png&h=a6d5eced&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cd1b30296dbec735e140b85323b047ea3ca00c3","tid":1056762,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實鄭俊英條撚樣幾時收皮<br />\n佢都唔係第一次啦喎<br />\n屌完咪算囉咁鐘意拍片做咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77b699536223b78ae6aad7569ff438f9c125211","tid":1056762,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cd1b30296dbec735e140b85323b047ea3ca00c3","tid":1056762,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實鄭俊英條撚樣幾時收皮<br />\n佢都唔係第一次啦喎<br />\n屌完咪算囉咁鐘意拍片做咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"拍完片仲咁鍾意分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c1dcf8d89f8539f0d9606632063ae0b3b029a7","tid":1056762,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAYXpYr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg